'''Teravaada''' ([[Sanskrit|Sanskrit]]: थेरवाद, [[Pali|Pali]], litarali "skuul a uola mongk") a wah branch a [[Budizim|Budizim]] we yuuz di tiichin a di [[Pali Kianan|Pali Kianan]], wah kalekshan a di uolis rikaad Budis tex, fii dakchrinal kuor, bot  iazwel ingkluud wah rich daivoersiti a chradishan ah praktis we divelop uoba ilang ischri a intarakshan wid difrah-difrah kolcha ah komiuniti. A di daminant faam a rilijan ina [[Kambuodia|Kambuodia]], [[Laus|Laus]], [[Mianmaa|Mianmaa]], [[Sri Langka|Sri Langka]], ah [[Tailan|Tailan]], ah ipraktis bai mainariti gruup in [[Banggladesh|Banggladesh]], [[Chaina|Chaina]], [[Malieja|Malieja]], [[Nepal|Nepal]], ah [[Vietnam|Vietnam]]. Den tu, di [[Dayaspora|dayaspora]] a aal demya gruup azwel kanvoert rong di wol praktis Theravaada Budizim.

